Text:
ESET gave a false positive on the keygen, but the file is clean, no virus here.

Thank you for this. ++

IMPORTANT (Readme V2) 
-Install SmartAssembly
-Unplug yourself of internet
-Open SmartAssembly
-Click Activate
-Paste the key if keygen (I think any edition will work, i did Professional)
-Click Activate Manually
-Copy the input, put it in the first textarea of keygen soft, copy the output and paste it in SmartAssembly
-Activate
-Plug back your internet, your free
